Title: Iron Sky
Writer: Jarmo Puskala (original concept), Johanna Sinisalo (based on a story by), Michael Kalesniko (screenplay by), Timo Vuorensola (screenplay by)
Actors: Julia Dietze, Christopher Kirby, Götz Otto, Udo Kier
Plot: In the last moments of World War II, a secret Nazi space program evaded destruction by fleeing to the Dark Side of the Moon. During 70 years of utter secrecy, the Nazis construct a gigantic space fortress with a massive armada of flying saucers.
Country: Finland, Germany, Australia, France, Norway, Belgium, Denmark, UK
Production: New Holland Pictures, Energia Productions, 27 Films Production, Blind Spot Pictures Oy
